title: CMDB Syncer: Services
agents: cmdb_syncer
catalog: app/cmdb_syncer
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the services of a CMDB Syncer installation, queried
 via the CMDB Syncer special agent.

 For each service it reports the status message. If the service reports
 an error the check becomes CRIT and shows the failure reason returned by
 the API. Additional detail messages are shown as OK results.

item:
 The name of the service.

discovery:
 One service is created for each CMDB Syncer service.
